            <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6">
                <p>The appointment log is a heart of this software. From loyalty program to inventory control and financial accounting, all is linked to the clients’ visits data. Just because of that, it’s very important to choose the most comfortable and functional solution on the market.</p>

                <p>INFOGROUP.ONLINE – is the real cloud platform. This means that several people can work with the log from different devices, including smartphones, at the same time. For instance, an employee, without leaving his working place, can make an appointment with a client for a haircut, and administrator and call center staff members will see that immediately. Online appointments also appear in the log instantly. This is all very important with a big client flow.</p>
            </div>
